SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 740
A bill to amend 1949 PA 300, entitled
"Michigan vehicle code,"
by amending sections 238, 806, and 810a (MCL 257.238, 257.806, and
257.810a), section 238 as amended by 2014 PA 291, section 806 as
amended by 2023 PA 129, and section 810a as amended by 1993 PA 300.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 238. (1) When an owner named in a certificate of title
2 creates a security interest in the vehicle described in the
3 certificate or in any accessory on the vehicle, all of the
4 following apply:
5 (a) The owner shall immediately execute an application in the
6 form prescribed by the department to name the holder of the
7 security interest on the certificate of title, showing the name and
