1 subsequently reassigns or transfers the motor vehicle lease
2 agreement or installment sale contract to the licensed dealer or
3 installment seller after a security interest is identified on the
4 application for title or the title for the vehicle, the person
5 shall provide written notice to the licensed dealer or installment
6 seller that the person does not retain a security interest or that
7 it has returned the security interest in the vehicle to the
8 licensed dealer or installment seller. If accompanied by a properly
9 completed application for title, the department shall accept the
