16 only if the selling dealer held an electronic title. A new or used
17 vehicle dealer that pays the fee under this subsection is not
18 subject to the fees in subsections (1) to (3) or section 810a. The
19 fee under this subsection must be deposited into the transportation
20 administration collection fund created under section 810b.
21 Sec. 810a. The Except as otherwise provided in section 806,
